trans-unit.source: Defines the SOAP fault codes that appear in a SOAP message when an error occurs while communicating with XML Web services using the SOAP version 1.2 protocol.
trans-unit.target: SOAP 버전 1.2 프로토콜을 사용 하는 XML 웹 서비스와 통신 하는 동안 오류가 발생 하는 경우에 SOAP 메시지에 표시 되는 SOAP 오류 코드를 정의 합니다.

trans-unit.source: A SOAP fault in version 1.2 of the SOAP specification contains a `Code` element and among other things an optional `Subcode` element.
trans-unit.target: SOAP 오류는 SOAP 사양의 버전 1.2에에서 포함 된 `Code` 요소와 선택적 `Subcode` 요소입니다.

trans-unit.source: The `Code` element is one of a pre-defined set of codes, informing a recipient that the cause of the error fell into one of five large error categories.
trans-unit.target: `Code` 요소는 미리 정의 된 코드, 오류의 원인이 다섯 가지 오류 범주 중 하나에 있는 받는 사람에 게 알리지 집합 중 하나입니다.

trans-unit.source: Those five fault codes are represented by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.ReceiverFaultCode>, <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.SenderFaultCode>, <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.VersionMismatchFaultCode>, <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.MustUnderstandFaultCode>, and <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.DataEncodingUnknownFaultCode> fields.
trans-unit.target: 이러한 다섯 가지 오류 코드는으로 표시 됩니다는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.ReceiverFaultCode>, <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.SenderFaultCode>, <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.VersionMismatchFaultCode>, <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.MustUnderstandFaultCode>, 및 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.DataEncodingUnknownFaultCode>필드.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.DataEncodingUnknownFaultCode> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.MustUnderstandFaultCode> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.VersionMismatchFaultCode> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.SenderFaultCode> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.ReceiverFaultCode>

trans-unit.source: The `Subcode` element allows the sender of the SOAP fault to provide an application-specific error code.
trans-unit.target: `Subcode` 요소를 사용 하면 응용 프로그램 관련 오류 코드를 제공 하는 SOAP 오류 보낸 사람입니다.

trans-unit.source: ASP.NET defines two such codes that are represented by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.RpcProcedureNotPresentFaultCode>, <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.RpcBadArgumentsFaultCode>, <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.EncodingMissingIDFaultCode>, and <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.EncodingUntypedValueFaultCode> fields.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET으로 표현 되는 이러한 두 개의 코드 정의 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.RpcProcedureNotPresentFaultCode>, <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.RpcBadArgumentsFaultCode>, <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.EncodingMissingIDFaultCode>, 및 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.EncodingUntypedValueFaultCode>필드.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.EncodingUntypedValueFaultCode> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.EncodingMissingIDFaultCode> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.RpcBadArgumentsFaultCode> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.RpcProcedureNotPresentFaultCode>

trans-unit.source: An XML Web service throwing an exception sets the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A> property, which represents the `Code` element, when a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException> or <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderException> class is created.
trans-unit.target: 집합 예외를 throw 하는 XML 웹 서비스는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A>속성을 나타내는 `Code` 때의 새 인스턴스 요소는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>또는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderException>클래스가 만들어집니다.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderException> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A>

trans-unit.source: That error is transmitted over the wire as a SOAP fault, which a .NET Framework client can catch as a <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException> or <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderException>.
trans-unit.target: 해당 오류는.NET Framework 클라이언트 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>또는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderException>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderException> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException> catch 할 수 있는 SOAP 오류, 네트워크를 통해 전송

trans-unit.source: Represents the SOAP version 1.2 <xref uid="langword_csharp_DataEncodingUnknown" name="DataEncodingUnknown" href=""></xref> fault code indicating the SOAP message is encoded in an unrecognized format.
trans-unit.target: SOAP 버전 1.2 나타냅니다 <xref uid="langword_csharp_DataEncodingUnknown" name="DataEncodingUnknown" href=""> </xref> SOAP 메시지를 나타내는 오류 코드는 인식할 수 없는 형식으로 인코딩되어 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: ASP.NET does not automatically throw a <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException> with the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A> property set to DataEncodingUnknownFaultCode.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET 자동으로 발생 하지 않습니다는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>와 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A>속성이 DataEncodingUnknownFaultCode로 설정 합니다.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: 추가할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Represents the fault code for missing ID in SOAP encoding data.
trans-unit.target: 누락 ID SOAP 인코딩 데이터에에서 대 한 오류 코드를 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: To be added.

trans-unit.source: Represents the SOAP version 1.2 <xref uid="langword_csharp_enc:UntypedValue" name="enc:UntypedValue" href=""></xref> fault subcode indicating that the SOAP message was RPC-encoded and the type name property of an encoded graph node was not specified.
trans-unit.target: SOAP 버전 1.2 나타냅니다 <xref uid="langword_csharp_enc:UntypedValue" name="enc:UntypedValue" href=""> </xref> 오류 하위 코드 되었음을 나타내는 RPC 인코딩된 SOAP 메시지를 인코딩된 그래프 노드의 유형 이름 속성을 지정 하지 않았습니다.

trans-unit.source: ASP.NET does not automatically throw a <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException> with the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property set to EncodingUntypedValueFaultCode.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET 자동으로 발생 하지 않습니다는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>와 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성이 EncodingUntypedValueFaultCode로 설정 합니다.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException> class has a <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Subcode%2A> property of type <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode> that represents the SOAP fault subcode.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>클래스에는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Subcode%2A>형식의 속성이 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode>SOAP 오류 하위 코드를 나타내는입니다.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Subcode%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property represents the URI for the actual SOAP fault subcode.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성은 실제 SOAP 오류 하위 코드에 대 한 URI를 나타냅니다.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: When setting the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to EncodingUntypedValueFaultCode, set the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.SenderFaultCode>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.SenderFaultCode>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.SenderFaultCode> 속성</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> 을 설정 하는 속성 EncodingUntypedValueFaultCode을</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> 설정 하는 경우

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: 추가할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Represents the SOAP version 1.2 <xref uid="langword_csharp_MustUnderstand" name="MustUnderstand" href=""></xref> fault code indicating a SOAP header marked with the <xref uid="langword_csharp_MustUnderstand" name="MustUnderstand" href=""></xref> attribute was not processed.
trans-unit.target: SOAP 버전 1.2 나타냅니다 <xref uid="langword_csharp_MustUnderstand" name="MustUnderstand" href=""> </xref> 로 표시 된 SOAP 헤더를 나타내는 오류 코드는 <xref uid="langword_csharp_MustUnderstand" name="MustUnderstand" href=""> </xref> 특성을 처리 하지 못했습니다.

trans-unit.source: Not all SOAP headers require processing by the recipient.
trans-unit.target: 모든 SOAP 헤더를 받는 사람이 처리를 해야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: However, if a SOAP header is marked with the `MustUnderstand` attribute equal to "true", processing is required.
trans-unit.target: 그러나 SOAP 헤더로 표시 되어 있으면는 `MustUnderstand` "true", 처리 같은 특성이 필요 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Failure to process the header when it resides within a SOAP 1.2 request generates a <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderException> with the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A> property set to MustUnderstandFaultCode.
trans-unit.target: SOAP 1.2 요청에 있는 헤더를 처리 하지 못한 경우 생성 된 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderException>와 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A>속성이 MustUnderstandFaultCode로 설정 합니다.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderException>

trans-unit.source: If the SOAP request resided within a SOAP 1.1 request, the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.MustUnderstandFaultCode?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: SOAP 요청 내 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A>속성이 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.MustUnderstandFaultCode?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.MustUnderstandFaultCode?displayProperty=fullName> 로 설정 되</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A> 는 SOAP 1.1 요청 내 상주 하는 경우

trans-unit.source: Both SOAP 1.1 and 1.2 define `MustUnderstand` SOAP fault codes differing only by the version of the SOAP protocol used to send the SOAP message.
trans-unit.target: SOAP 1.1 및 1.2를 모두 정의 `MustUnderstand` SOAP 프로토콜의 버전 동작만 다른 SOAP 오류 코드는 SOAP 메시지를 보내는 데 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: This field represents the SOAP 1.2 version, and the SOAP 1.1 version is represented by <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.MustUnderstandFaultCode?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: 이 필드는 SOAP 1.2 버전 나타냅니다 및 SOAP 1.1 버전 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.MustUnderstandFaultCode?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.MustUnderstandFaultCode?displayProperty=fullName> 으로 나타납니다.

trans-unit.source: The two fields map to different qualified names, but you can check whether the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A> property is either one of the fault codes by calling the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.IsMustUnderstandFaultCode%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 두 필드가 다른 정규화 된 이름에 매핑되는 하지만 확인할 수 있는지 여부를 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A>호출 하 여 오류 코드 중 하나에 대 한 속성을는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.IsMustUnderstandFaultCode%2A>메서드.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.IsMustUnderstandFaultCode%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: 추가할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Represents the SOAP version 1.2 <xref uid="langword_csharp_Receiver" name="Receiver" href=""></xref> fault code indicating an error occurred during the processing of a client call on the server due to a problem with the recipient.
trans-unit.target: SOAP 버전 1.2 나타냅니다 <xref uid="langword_csharp_Receiver" name="Receiver" href=""> </xref> 수신자 관련 문제로 인해 서버에서 클라이언트 호출을 처리 하는 동안 오류 코드에서 오류가 발생 했습니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException> is thrown with the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A> property set to ReceiverFaultCode when a server is called and it could not respond to a request due to network problems.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>함께 발생는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A>속성이 서버 라고 하 고 네트워크 문제로 인해 요청에 응답할 수 없는 경우 ReceiverFaultCode로 설정 합니다.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>

trans-unit.source: Typically, with this type of exception, the client call may succeed later.
trans-unit.target: 일반적으로으로이 유형의 예외를 사용 하 여 클라이언트 호출을 나중에 성공할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The `Receiver` SOAP fault code is similar to the `Server` fault code, which is represented by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.ServerFaultCode> field, but the `Server` fault code is used when the SOAP request is sent using SOAP 1.1.
trans-unit.target: `Receiver` SOAP 오류 코드는 비슷합니다는 `Server` 오류 코드가 요소로 표시 되는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.ServerFaultCode>필드 이지만 `Server` SOAP 1.1을 사용 하 여 SOAP 요청을 보내면 오류 코드를 사용 합니다.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.ServerFaultCode>

trans-unit.source: To check whether the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A> property is either the `Receiver` or `Server` SOAP fault codes, call the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.IsServerFaultCode%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 확인 하려면 여부는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A>속성이 `Receiver` 또는 `Server` SOAP 오류 코드, 호출의 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.IsServerFaultCode%2A>메서드.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.IsServerFaultCode%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: 추가할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Represents the SOAP version 1.2 <xref uid="langword_csharp_rpc:BadArguments" name="rpc:BadArguments" href=""></xref> fault subcode indicating that arguments sent to the XML Web service method were incorrect or could not be parsed.
trans-unit.target: SOAP 버전 1.2 나타냅니다 <xref uid="langword_csharp_rpc:BadArguments" name="rpc:BadArguments" href=""> </xref> 오류 하위 코드가 나타내는 XML 웹 서비스 메서드에 전달 된 인수의 잘못 되었음을 또는 분석할 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: ASP.NET does not automatically throw a <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException> with the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property set to RpcBadArgumentsFaultCode.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET 자동으로 발생 하지 않습니다는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>와 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성이 RpcBadArgumentsFaultCode로 설정 합니다.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException> class has a <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Subcode%2A> property of type <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode> that represents the SOAP fault subcode.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>클래스에는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Subcode%2A>형식의 속성이 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode>SOAP 오류 하위 코드를 나타내는입니다.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Subcode%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property represents the URI for the actual SOAP fault subcode.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성은 실제 SOAP 오류 하위 코드에 대 한 URI를 나타냅니다.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: When setting the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to RpcBadArgumentsFaultCode, set the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.SenderFaultCode>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.SenderFaultCode>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.SenderFaultCode> 속성</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> 을 설정 하는 속성 RpcBadArgumentsFaultCode을</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> 설정 하는 경우

trans-unit.target: SOAP 버전 1.2 나타냅니다 <xref uid="langword_csharp_rpc:ProcedureNotPresent" name="rpc:ProcedureNotPresent" href=""> </xref> XML 웹 서비스를 나타내는 오류 하위 코드 요청된 XML 웹 서비스 메서드를 지원 하지 않습니다.

trans-unit.target: ASP.NET 자동으로 발생 하지 않습니다는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>와 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성이 RpcProcedureNotPresentFaultCode로 설정 합니다.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException> class has a <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Subcode%2A> property of type <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode> that represents the SOAP fault subcode.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>클래스에는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Subcode%2A>형식의 속성이 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode>SOAP 오류 하위 코드를 나타내는입니다.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Subcode%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property represents the URI for the actual SOAP fault subcode.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성은 실제 SOAP 오류 하위 코드에 대 한 URI를 나타냅니다.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: When setting the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to RpcProcedureNotPresentFaultCode, set the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.SenderFaultCode>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.SenderFaultCode>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.Soap12FaultCodes.SenderFaultCode> 속성</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> 을 설정 하는 속성 RpcProcedureNotPresentFaultCode을</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapFaultSubcode.Code%2A?displayProperty=fullName> 설정 하는 경우

trans-unit.source: Represents the SOAP version 1.2 <xref uid="langword_csharp_Sender" name="Sender" href=""></xref> fault code indicating a client call was not formatted correctly or did not contain the appropriate information.
trans-unit.target: SOAP 버전 1.2 나타냅니다 <xref uid="langword_csharp_Sender" name="Sender" href=""> </xref> 클라이언트 호출을 나타내는 오류 코드 형식이 올바르지 않습니다. 또는 적절 한 정보가 포함 되어 있지 않으면입니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException> is thrown with the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A> property set to SenderFaultCode when a SOAP 1.2 request is malformed or a parameter is missing.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>함께 발생는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A>속성이 SOAP 1.2 요청 형식이 잘못 되었거나 매개 변수가 없는 경우 SenderFaultCode로 설정 합니다.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException>

trans-unit.source: The `Sender` SOAP fault code is similar to the `Client` fault code, which is represented by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.ClientFaultCode> field, but the `Client` fault code is used when the SOAP request is sent using SOAP 1.1.
trans-unit.target: `Sender` SOAP 오류 코드는 비슷합니다는 `Client` 오류 코드가 요소로 표시 되는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.ClientFaultCode>필드 이지만 `Client` SOAP 1.1을 사용 하 여 SOAP 요청을 보내면 오류 코드를 사용 합니다.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.ClientFaultCode>

trans-unit.source: To check whether the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A> property is either the `Sender` or `Client` SOAP fault codes, call the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.IsClientFaultCode%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 확인 하려면 여부는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A>속성이 `Sender` 또는 `Client` SOAP 오류 코드, 호출의 <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.IsClientFaultCode%2A>메서드.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.IsClientFaultCode%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapException.Code%2A>

trans-unit.source: Represents the SOAP version 1.2 <xref uid="langword_csharp_VersionMismatch" name="VersionMismatch" href=""></xref> fault code indicating the XML Web service expected SOAP messages conforming to the SOAP 1.2 specification, yet received one conforming to SOAP 1.1.
trans-unit.target: SOAP 버전 1.2 나타냅니다 <xref uid="langword_csharp_VersionMismatch" name="VersionMismatch" href=""> </xref> XML 웹 서비스를 나타내는 오류 코드는 SOAP 1.2 사양에 맞는 SOAP 메시지를 예상 아직 SOAP 1.1을 따르는 나타났습니다.
